$$
f(y)=\left\{\begin{array}{rr}
\frac{1}{2}e^{-\frac{y}{2}},&y>0\\
0,&y\leq0
\end{array}\right.
$$

那么$X$和$2Y$的联合概率密度为____A.$$
f(x, y)=\left\{\begin{array}{rc}
\frac{1}{2} e^{-y}, & 0<x<2, \quad y>0, \\
0, & \text { 其他. }
\end{array}\right.
$$B.$$
f(x, y)=\left\{\begin{array}{rc}
\frac{1}{4} e^{-\frac{y}{4}}, & 0<x<1, \quad y>0, \\
0, & \text { 其他. }
\end{array}\right.
$$C.$$
f(x, y)=\left\{\begin{array}{cc}
\frac{1}{2} e^{-\frac{y}{2}}, & 0<x<1, \quad y>0, \\
0, & \text { 其他. }
\end{array}\right.
$$D.$$
f(x, y)=\left\{\begin{array}{rc}
\frac{1}{4} e^{-\frac{y}{2}}, & 0<x<2, \quad y>0, \\
0, & \text { 其他. }
\end{array}\right.
$$

某工厂生产一批滚珠,其直径$X$服从正态分布$N\left(\mu,\sigma^{2}\right)$,随机抽取20个滚珠,测得样本均值记为$\bar{x}$,样本方差记为$s^{2}$,则$\mu$的单侧置信下限、$\sigma^{2}$单侧置信上限分别为(置信度都为$1-\alpha$)____A.$$
\bar{x}-\frac{s}{\sqrt{20}} t_{\alpha}(19), \quad \frac{19 s^{2}}{\chi_{1-\alpha}^{2}(19)}
