$$C.$$
\bar{x}-\frac{s}{\sqrt{20}} t_{\alpha}(19), \quad \frac{19 s^{2}}{\chi_{\alpha}^{2}(19)}
$$D.$$
\bar{x}-\frac{\sigma}{\sqrt{20}} u_{\alpha}, \quad \frac{19 s^{2}}{\chi_{\alpha}^{2}(19)}
$$

